title: Zayn Malik's new single 'Still Got Time' is a lonely-girl anthem
text:
Zayn Malik's new single 'Still Got Time' is a lonely-girl anthem Maeve McDermott , USATODAY 11:58 a.m. ET March 24, 2017 A post shared by Zayn Malik (@zayn) on Mar 21, 2017 at 8:08am PDT 
For all the Zayn Malik fans still searching for their special someone, the pop star has a hopeful message: "Just stop lookin' for love, girl you know you still got time." 
The Pillowtalk singer, currently in a relationship with Gigi Hadid , released his latest single Still Got Time on Thursday, a collaboration with PARTYNEXTDOOR. 
The track marks the first time the two R&B crooners have worked together, produced by Frank Dukes (who previously collaborated with Rihanna, Kanye West, Drake and Future) and co-produced by Murda Beatz.
